  "_comment_architecture": [
    "EUDR Due Diligence Statement notification.",
    "Static product attributes (the regulatoryInformation block, eudr: classification",
    "and the assessment outcome — deforestationFreeDate / legallyHarvested / riskLevel /",
    "verificationMethod) live INSIDE masterDataAvailableFor on the product entry.",
    "Event-level slot is reserved for what happened (the operator notifying / submitting).",
    "",
    "HTTP header for EPCIS capture:",
    "  GS1-Extensions: dpp=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/common/core/,eudr=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/eu/eudr/",
    "",
    "See: core/docs/EPCIS_MASTERDATA_AND_EXTENSIONS.md for the full reference.",
    "See: GS1 Germany EUDR Guideline V1.11 Section 4.2 for masterDataAvailableFor patterns.",
    "GS1 demo prefix 952 (7-digit GCP: 9521234)."
  ],
